          </p>
          <p>
            Now I write code. But I'm still doing the same thing I've always done: helping people run better businesses.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- What I Bring -->
      <div class="mb-20">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-medium text-accent-blue uppercase tracking-wide mb-8">What I Bring</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-border-subtle bg-bg-secondary/30">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent-purple/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-accent-purple text-lg">ðŸ“Š</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-text-primary font-medium mb-2">Business</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">I've run businesses, not just built websites for them. I understand margins, customers, and the reality of limited time and budget.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-border-subtle bg-bg-secondary/30">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent-blue/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-accent-blue text-lg">ðŸ’»</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-text-primary font-medium mb-2">Technology</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">Modern tools, clean code, no bloat. I build fast, maintainable systems that actually solve problemsâ€”not create new ones.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-border-subtle bg-bg-secondary/30">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent-pink/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-accent-pink text-lg">ðŸŽ“</span>
